            "datePublished": "11 Aug 2010 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "Expanded and remastered deluxe 2CD reissue of the debut album by Coppice Halifax, 1983. Originally only issued as four tracks for free download (as part of Project 168 Part 2 in 2006) and then on a promotional run of 50 copies with two bonus tracks (at EED later in 2006), this comprehensive edition contains all 6 tracks from the EED version, remastered, as well as 5 previously unreleased tracks, a live track and new artwork. All material was remastered from the original session tapes, and for collectors a limited edition cassette version has been faithfully produced in tandem with this digital release.",
            "credits": "released August 11, 2010\nW/P by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at 114RKD, 2006. This is Milieu Music number MMD012. Updated May 2019 / Domitus Cultoribus Orbis.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
