            "item_id": 835693340,
            "art_id": 1494999051,
            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "31 May 2016 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "The second release in the RIPETIS / REITERATED catalog of remixes and reconfigurations is ALKEMIISTO, a nine-track collection of selected remix approaches to Deep Earth by five of the most talented musicians I have the pleasure to know. Zwei Kreise, known previously as Axs, appears twice with a beat-based mix of Vintro and a beatless mix of Malaperis. Two of the denser mixes on ALKEMIISTO come from aural sculptor Arjen Schat, also known as Ohrwert. Fah appears here under his less-used Ambigen moniker, contributing two atmospheric pieces created with his custom-designed generative ambient software. Perhaps the most conventional sounding of all the mixes is the EARTH 4 reconstitution Cielarkus, courtesy of The Green Kingdom, while the album closes with a nearly half-hour excursion into Vintro by Orson Throb. An appropriate counterpoint to the year's fruits in the series, and a solid full-length album of deep and experimental techno works by some of the best minds in the market today.",
            "credits": "released May 31, 2016\nWritten by Brian Grainger. Produced and remixed by the credited artists. Mastered by The Analog Botanist at Botany Bay, May 2016. Cover photography by Brian Grainger. This is Milieu Music number RIPETIS 2. © + ℗ Milieu Music, 2016. All rights reserved.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a1494999051_0",
