            "item_id": 4148990972,
            "art_id": 3529077376,
            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "06 Nov 2020 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "A Halifaxian transfiguration of \"Shimmering Skull Raga\" from my White Kingdoms album, produced and published under my birthname. This mix was drafted for the occasion of the 10th anniversary expanded reissue of White Kingdoms, and is being made available digitally by itself for listeners who do not wish to buy a deluxe multi-disc edition in order to obtain a new CH recording. It was created using the original four-track session tapes from White Kingdoms as the sole audio source, and is in alignment with the many prior CH remixes of Milieu and BG recordings, previously collected as Arborist's Excavations, that appear on the Arboreal Digest reissue catalog entries.\nTo purchase this mix, as well as the expanded White Kingdoms album, on a 3xCD-R set, please visit the Brian Grainger Bandcamp page:  briangrainger.bandcamp.com/album/white-kingdoms-expanded-reissue",
            "credits": "released November 6, 2020\nW/P by Brian Grainger. Remixed and produced by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at White Pillar, Summer 2020, using White Kingdoms as the sole audio source. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. Photography by Brian, Foxhill 2009. Interpolation and text by ABM&D. This is Milieu Music number AD46B, a supplemental digital-only entry in the Arboreal Digest reissue catalog.  milieu-music.com analogbotany.com",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a3529077376_0",
            "trackinfo": [
                {
                    "title": "Shimmering Skull Raga [An Extract Of Keystone Flowers]",
