            "datePublished": "16 Sep 2016 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "...EARTH 15 in the DEEP EARTH series...\nHavanta naskiĝis atestanto al la Transfiguriĝo de tero, malgranda kargo ŝipo komencas devenon de la supra surfaco de la suba surfaco. Nove frostigita nigra stepo cedas silente al la veturilo kaj liaj radoj. Internaj sistemoj vicigi, agordi itineron kaj pravalorizi.",
            "credits": "released September 16, 2016\nW/P by Brian Grainger. Principally performed and recorded at Botany Bay, Summer 2016, with final gloss and production at White Pillar Workshop, Autumn 2016. These tracks constitute the final recordings made at Botany Bay before the studio closed. Recorded live, without overdubs, using a no-input assemblage of three Moog FX units, an Alesis Quadraverb, a Nady analog delay, a Boss SL20 and a Mackie ProFX8. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number [EARTH 15], and 15th in the ongoing DEEP EARTH series. Photography by Brian, Columbia 2016.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
