            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "01 May 2014 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "A live-in-studio session at Botany Bay, from October 2011. Two hours of deep techno - the first hour being original material (both released and unreleased), and the second hour being a selection of CH remixes. Originally recorded for Contemporary Vision's radio show.\nSection A: Constructed\n00:00 Clear\n02:38 Autumn Rebuild\n10:34 Botany Bay / Compost\n16:45 H-Tape\n23:28 Lake Busbee\n33:40 Humid Acre\n41:30 Halifaxian II\n48:42 Midnight Snack [Carbonated]\n58:30 Dusk [Live Alteration]\nSection B: Recycled\n61:25 Electricwest - Scarlet [Cmx]\n74:06 Arbee - Couvert [Coppice Halifax Rebuild]\n81:20 Other Heights - As We Are [Bubbling Swamp Cmx]\n89:00 Mikrokristal - Ta-Ta [Disphenoid Cmx]\n97:50 Textural Being - Tiefenwahrnehmung [Coppice Halifax Cmx 2b]\n103:45 Monoaxial - Pale [Cmx]",
            "credits": "released May 1, 2014\nW/P by Brian Grainger, except where noted. Performed and recorded at Botany Bay, October 2011. This is Milieu Music number MMLP12.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a2436341670_0",
