            "about": "BCR DUB is a digital release of the CH excavation for BLUE COUNTRY RAIN by Brian Grainger, drafted for the expanded reissue of the drone double-album SILVER HORNS HEARD OVER GREEN HILLS, available in a limited edition 3xCD-R set:  briangrainger.bandcamp.com/album/silver-horns-heard-over-green-hills-expanded-reissue",
            "credits": "released May 30, 2017\nWritten by Brian Grainger / Produced & Remixed by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at White Pillar Workshop, Summer 2017. Text and design by ABM&D. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number AD24B.",
