            "about": "BLUEWEATHER is a CH excavation of IN BLUE FIELDS by Milieu, drafted for the 10th anniversary expanded reissue of PHOSPHENE WEATHER, available (with this mix included) on a limited edition 2xCD-R set here:  milieumusic.bandcamp.com/album/phosphene-weather-10th-anniversary-expanded-reissue\nThis digital release is to make the mix available to CH listeners who are, for whatever reason, uninterested in ordering a Milieu album in order to obtain this remix.",
            "credits": "released November 21, 2019\nWritten by Milieu / Produced & Remixed by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at White Pillar Workshop, Autumn 2019. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number AD50B. Text and design mutation by ABM&D.",
