            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "13 Jan 2022 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "I am standing by a river\nBeneath the sun\nBoundlessness",
            "credits": "released January 13, 2022\nW/P by Brian Grainger. Recorded at White Pillar, January 13th 2022 using 4x Aeolian-tuned Euclidean sequencers, two sinewaves from self-oscillating low-pass filters, a granular synthesizer and a digital tape organ tuned to whole tone, supplemented by a sampled kick drum from a Yamaha MR-10 drum machine and a sampled bass from an Arturia Microfreak. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. Photograph by Brian, 2021. Text and design by ABM&D, recalling 843. This is Milieu Music number ABX121. (C) + (P) Oscillog ASCAP 2022. All nights preserved.",
