            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "17 May 2014 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "For RX17, the Static Pharming series produces Cloudburst, an overcast piece that layers together cloudy synth drones and tape-saturated bass. Growing gradually more misty and humidified, Cloudburst eventually reveals throbbing rhythmic shapes inside the haze that emerge with bright colors and an undeniable house-inflected groove.",
            "credits": "released May 17, 2014\nW/P by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at Botany Bay, April 2014. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number RX17, and 17th in the ongoing Static Pharming series.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a2783821912_0",
