            "about": "A live session of sonic reconstitution, recorded at Botany Bay on February 8th, 2013.\n00:00 R5\n03:02 Cedar Mast V\n05:38 Dilate\n06:17 Smoker's Lux [Clove Cigarettes Mix]\n09:36 Pharma C\n15:46 Amber Castles\n16:55 Helial Phases\n19:12 Malibu\n21:15 Dry\n21:43 Repeat Unit\n26:14 Ganymede\n27:53 Nuclear Dawn [Amb]\n29:29 Night Grove\n33:36 F3DC1B\n34:45 Antu\n36:11 Dusk 3\n38:07 The Gray Man\n38:55 Forest\n47:53 Hallex [Saturated]\n48:48 Dirt\n49:42 Smoky Acre\n53:16 Reflector",
            "credits": "released June 25, 2014\nAll music written and produced by Coppice Halifax. Performed at Botany Bay, February 8, 2013. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number MMLP13.",
