                "Cleveland"
            ],
            "item_id": 2553029029,
            "art_id": 2984687354,
            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "07 Aug 2020 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "DEEPWOODS MIXTURE is a live set of Halifaxian composted techno, mulched together from various different releases and tape sessions into a singular, pulsing entity, similar in approach to COMPOSTING TECHNIQUES FOR MORE FRUITFUL GARDENING, although a bit more in the 4/4 techno department. Originally, this session was laid to tape at the invitation of the Deep Breakfast podcast series in Italy, but until now it has been unavailable in lossless quality, or on any physical edition. Listeners are encouraged to explore the DEEPWOODS MIXTURE in a variety of settings, from headphones, to bedtime, from cruising in a car to sitting on a porch. Substance-enhanced, but never derived, 100% pure. Does what it says on the tin.",
            "credits": "released August 7, 2020\nW/P by Brian Grainger. Recorded at White Pillar, Winter 2019/2020. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. Text, photography and design by ABM&D. This is Milieu Music number ABX111.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a2984687354_0",
