            "datePublished": "11 Aug 2010 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "Depth Analysis is a 2 track EP expansion of the Coppice Halifax half of The Deep Tapes, a split album with The House In The Woods (aka Pye Corner Audio). It contains two alternate versions of tracks on The Deep Tapes, taking the abyssal approach just a little bit deeper...",
            "credits": "released August 11, 2010\nW/P by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at 114RKD, 2010. This is Milieu Music number MML073.",
