            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "19 Mar 2019 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "...EARTH 39 in YEAR FOUR of the DEEP EARTH series...\nSciante tiam, ke ni vere estas en la mallumo, lumo flagras en milionoj da neeviteblaj fendoj ĉirkaŭ ni. I ĉiam estis tie, ni nur fermis niajn okulojn.\nLIMITED PHYSICAL EDITION AVAILABLE AT DEEP EARTH:  malfokusita.bandcamp.com/album/disradii",
            "credits": "released March 19, 2019\nW/P by Brian Grainger. Recorded live at the White Pillar Workshop, March 11 2019, using a DOD FX75B flanger as the sole input source, processed through the veins of an Alesis Quadraverb resonator, Pioneer SR202W spring reverb box, Digitech WH-4 pitch shifter, Boss RV-3 digital reverb, BBE Two Timer analog delay and two custom DSP patches onboard the Peavey FX2 24-channel mixing board. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number EARTH 39, and 39th in the Deep Earth series.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a0067855290_0",
            "trackinfo": [
                {
                    "title": "Disradii",
                    "duration": "30:53",
                    "lyrics": null,
                    "label": "Milieu Music Digital",
                    "track_id": 1059747272,
                    "track_num": "1",
                    "artist": "Coppice Halifax",
                    "url": "https://coppicehalifax.bandcamp.com/track/disradii",
                    "trackCoverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a0067855290_0",
                    "art_id": 67855290,
                    "about": null,
                    "credits": "from Disradii / Emit, released March 19, 2019",
                    "license": "all rights reserved"
                }
            ]
        },
