            "datePublished": "21 Nov 2019 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "DUNESURFER is a digital release for the CH excavation of SAND DUNES by Milieu, drafted in celebration/support of the expanded and remastered 2xCD-R album BRITTLE PAPER CATHEDRALS, available in a limited edition here:  milieumusic.bandcamp.com/album/brittle-paper-cathedrals-expanded-remastered",
            "credits": "released November 21, 2019\nWritten by Milieu / Produced & Remixed by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at White Pillar Workshop, Autumn 2018. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. Text and design by ABM&D. This is Milieu Music number AD38B.",
