            "is_preorder": false,
            "datePublished": "03 Mar 2014 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "Eluvian is the 15th Static Pharming EP, built entirely out of field recordings. Woodside trains, rocks in mud and fireworks coalesce together through a Halifaxian sound design that pieces together an alien obelisk out of thin air. Organic and overgrown, but still totally rhythmic and faithful to the dub techno template.",
            "credits": "released March 3, 2014\nW/P by Coppice Halifax. Recorded at Botany Bay, February 2014. Mastered by The Analog Botanist. This is Milieu Music number RX15, 15th in the ongoing Static Pharming series.",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
            "coverUrl_0": "https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a2651194379_0",
