            "about": "Performed and recorded completely live at Foxhill for an invite-only party of friends and family in 2010. Organically growing and cross-pollinating giant dub techno structures using source from the Analog Botany sessions, earlier CH material and even unreleased tracks. A dense, winding hour-long set that blends dozens of CH tracks seamlessly with a constant groove and atmosphere at the forefront.",
